  "detailed_description": "<h1>Also recommended for you</h1><p></p><br><h1>Also recommended for you</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/fdcbe25b8c9ff434d6b039b8d37833df.poster.avif?t=1689341601\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/fdcbe25b8c9ff434d6b039b8d37833df.webm?t=1689341601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/fdcbe25b8c9ff434d6b039b8d37833df.mp4?t=1689341601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Hidden Mars  is a game to search for the famous cat of space.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/bd4fafeaf4667669e337263800fdfb46.poster.avif?t=1689341601\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/bd4fafeaf4667669e337263800fdfb46.webm?t=1689341601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/bd4fafeaf4667669e337263800fdfb46.mp4?t=1689341601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's a fun quest for Felicat among rockets and space race Mars rovers. It's a game with black and white drawings and illustrations.<br><br>Find the cat Felicat.<br>You can find more than 100 hidden Felicats<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/d09e0ca783f241f0c366b41bbd962a8c.poster.avif?t=1689341601\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/d09e0ca783f241f0c366b41bbd962a8c.webm?t=1689341601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/d09e0ca783f241f0c366b41bbd962a8c.mp4?t=1689341601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Feature Zoom In and Zom Out for more details </strong><br><br><br><strong>Important information</strong><br><br><strong>•\tPress “M” for  mode Mars</strong><br><strong>•\tPress Del and Esc to reset game.</strong><br><br>Be patient!<br>Hold the anxiety!<br>Relax and travel through the space to find the astronaut felicat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1689341601\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1689341601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222750/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1689341601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
